org.zaproxy.zap.view.messagelocation

Interface MessageLocationProducerFocusListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractMessageLocationsPanel.MessageLocationsFocusListener

    public interface MessageLocationProducerFocusListener
extends EventListener
    An EventListener that allows to listen to MessageLocationProducerFocusEvent.

    Used to listen to changes in the focus of MessageLocationProducers and propagate the event with the custom format.

    Since:
    2.4.0
    See Also:
    MessageLocationProducerFocusEvent, MessageLocationProducer
